main event: A civilian reported observing an object in the sky over Dayton, Ohio on January 23, 1962.
interesting points: The object had varied shapes, including a 'theatre marquee' with dark objects moving across it, and lights that would go out and on again.
The object was in contact with a person from Winchester, Kentucky who was flying an aircraft with a large advertising sign on the bottom.
The object's lights would go out and on again as the aircraft flew.
sighted object: an object with varied shapes and lights
